10#include <stdio.h>
11#include "internal/cryptlib.h"
12#include <openssl/asn1.h>
13#include <openssl/objects.h>
14#include <openssl/evp.h>
15#include <openssl/x509.h>
16#include "internal/x509_int.h"
17
18int X509_REQ_set_version(X509_REQ *x, long version)
19{
20 if (x == NULL)
21 return 0;
22 x->req_info.enc.modified = 1;
23 return ASN1_INTEGER_set(x->req_info.version, version);
24}
25
26int X509_REQ_set_subject_name(X509_REQ *x, X509_NAME *name)
27{
28 if (x == NULL)
29 return 0;
30 x->req_info.enc.modified = 1;
31 return X509_NAME_set(&x->req_info.subject, name);
32}
33
34int X509_REQ_set_pubkey(X509_REQ *x, EVP_PKEY *pkey)
35{
36 if (x == NULL)
37 return 0;
38 x->req_info.enc.modified = 1;
39 return X509_PUBKEY_set(&x->req_info.pubkey, pkey);
40}
